    "step": {
      "warmup": "Gushyushya amajwi",
      "warmup_inst": "Irekure ukoresheje yawns, iminwa (brrr), hamwe na hum yoroshye muminota. Ntibikenewe ko wandika - ni ukuruhura umuhogo mbere yo kuririmba.",
